  <div class="container mt-5 mb-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to BeatBuddy!</h1>
      <p class="lead">Your Personalized Music Journey Awaits</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-10">
        <div class="card mb-3">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <a href="/toptracks"><h2 class="card-title">Explore Your Top Tracks</h2></a> 
            <p>Rediscover old favorites and find new tunes tailored to your taste, all based on your Spotify listening history.</p>
          </div>
