        </div>

        <div class="card mb-3">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <h2 class="card-title">Connect and Share</h2>
            <p>Share your music discoveries and concert plans with friends, enhancing your social music experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="my-4 text-center">
          <a href="/spotifylogin" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Connect Your Spotify Account and Begin</a>
